name: dimcloud
description: soundcloud.com dark material theme with mixes of orange color. npm config only for private sass retributing.

scripts.build: if [ ! -f build.sh ]; then echo "No build.sh found. Trying to download it from raw.githubusercontent.com"; wget -O build.sh "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mira-ta/dimcloud/master/build.sh"; chmod +x build.sh; fi; ./build.sh
